                <sv:property sv:name="${rootArtifactId.replace($hyphen,$underscore)}:body" sv:type="String">
                    <sv:value>&lt;div id="content_main"&gt; &lt;p&gt;Hippo products
                        enable you to optimize information management in your organization. Our
                        current offering exists out of three products:&lt;/p&gt;
                        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a
                        href="http://www.onehippo.com/en/products,hippo-cms/index.html"&gt;Hippo
                        CMS&lt;/a&gt;: for publishing web and intranet content. This native
                        XML content management system is suited for organizations that have large
                        amounts of unstructured data. Hippo CMS allows you to organize and structure
                        your content and makes content retrieval easier.&lt;/p&gt;
                        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a
                        href="http://www.onehippo.com/en/products,hippo-portal/index.html"&gt;Hippo
                        Portal:&lt;/a&gt; streamlines and authorizes various information
                        sources in your company. The portal technology (JSR-168) enables you to
                        integrate back-office applications without losing control. It allows for
                        personalisation and extensive rights management.&lt;/p&gt;
                        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a
                        href="http://www.onehippo.com/en/products,documentmanagement/index.html"&gt;Hippo
                        Document Management (CDM)&lt;/a&gt;: is suited for maintaining
                        technical documentation (compound documents). It can handle complex XML
                        structures and still allows for lightning fast retrieval (a big plus against
                        other players in this field).&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;</sv:value>
